		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2009/index.html">SLE 2009</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2009/paper18.html">Language Boxes: Bending the Host Language with Modular Language Changes</a></em> (<a href="../profile/LukasRenggli.html">Lukas Renggli</a>, <a href="../profile/MarcusDenker.html">Marcus Denker</a>, <a href="../profile/OscarNierstrasz.html"><span class="info">Oscar Nierstrasz</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014/paper04.html">Bounded Seas: Island Parsing Without Shipwrecks</a></em> (<a href="../profile/JanKurš.html">Jan Kurš</a>, <a href="../profile/MirceaLungu.html">Mircea Lungu</a>, <a href="../profile/OscarNierstrasz.html"><span class="info">Oscar Nierstrasz</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014/paper06.html">The Moldable Debugger: A Framework for Developing Domain-Specific Debuggers</a></em> (<a href="../profile/AndreiChiș.html">Andrei Chiș</a>, <a href="../profile/TudorGîrba.html">Tudor Gîrba</a>, <a href="../profile/OscarNierstrasz.html"><span class="info">Oscar Nierstrasz</span></a>) </li>
