<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014s/index.html">SLE 2014 SI</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2014s/paper05.html">Practical domain-specific debuggers using the Moldable Debugger framework</a></em> (<a href="../profile/AndreiChiș.html">Andrei Chiș</a>, <a href="../profile/MarcusDenker.html">Marcus Denker</a>, <a href="../profile/TudorGîrba.html">Tudor Gîrba</a>, <a href="../profile/OscarNierstrasz.html"><span class="info">Oscar Nierstrasz</span></a>) </li>
